ry:Colombian male telenovela actors]]\n[[Category:Colombian male television actors]]\n[[Category:1964 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Male actors of Italian descent]]\n", "text_old": "{{BLP sources|date=August 2015}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name = Miguel Varoni\n| image = File:Miguel+Varoni+Arrivals+Billboard+Latin+Music+6peQxrw1tWll.jpg\n| imagesize = \n| caption = \n| birth_name = Miguel Am\u00e9rico Belloto Guti\u00e9rrez\n| birth_date = {{Birth date and age|1964|12|11}}\n| birth_place = [[Buenos Aires]], [[Argentina]]<ref>http://www.formulatv.com/personas/1674/gary-forero/ Gary Forero</ref> \n| othername = \n| website =\n| parents = Americo Bellotto (father)<br> [[Teresa Guti\u00e9rrez]] (mother)\n| spouse = [[Catherine Siachoque]] (1997\u2013present)\n| occupation = Actor, director\n| years_active = 1986-present\n| notable role = \n}}\n\n'''Miguel Varoni''' (born '''Miguel Am\u00e9rico Belloto Guti\u00e9rrez'''; December 11, 1964) is a Colombian-Argentinian [[Television presenter|host]], [[actor]] and [[film director|director]]. He is married to [[Colombia]]n actress [[Catherine Siachoque]].\nHe is the son of the actress [[Teresa Guti\u00e9rrez]].\n\n== Filmography ==\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[imdbtitle:0497939|Mi abuelo, mi pap\u00e1 y yo]]''\n| Eduardo\n| \n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Ladr\u00f3n que roba a ladr\u00f3n]]''\n| Emilio L\u00f3pez\n| \n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Sin tetas no hay para\u00edso]]''\n| Dr. Mauricio Contento\n| \n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[M\u00e1s sabe el diablo|M\u00e1s sabe el diablo: El primer golpe]]''\n| Martin Acero / El Hierro\n| Direct-to-DVD; prequel to novela\n|-\n|}\n\n=== Television ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1986\n| ''[[:es:Gallito Ram\u00edrez|Gallito Ram\u00edrez]]''\n| Arturo Sanclemente\n| \n|-\n| 1988\n| ''[[:es:Garzas al amanecer|Garzas al amanecer]]''\n| Chepe