l (2017), ''When the World Seemed New:  George H. W. Bush and the End of the Cold War'', New York:  Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, {{ISBN|978-0547423067}} .\n*George Galloway and Bob Wylie, ''Downfall: The Ceau\u0219escus and the Romanian Revolution'', 1991, Futura Publications, London. {{ISBN|0-7088-5003-0}}\n*{{in lang|ro}} Marius Mioc, ''[https://web.archive.org/web/20060619080849/http://timisoara.com/timisoara/revoluti.htm Revolu\u021bia din Timi\u0219oara], a\u0219a cum a fost'', 1997, Brumar Publishing House, Timi\u0219oara (in Romanian)\n*{{in lang|ro}} Marius Mioc, ''[http://procesulcomunismului.com/marturii/fonduri/mmioc/anticomrev/default.asp.htm The anticommunist Romanian Revolution] of 1989'', Marineasa Publishing House, Timi\u0219oara 2002\n*{{in lang|ro}} Marian Oprea, \"Au trecut 15 ani \u2013 Conspira\u021bia Securit\u0103\u021bii\" (\"After 15 years \u2013 the conspiracy of Securitate\"), [https://web.archive.org/web/20050209133319/http://www.lumeam.ro/nr10_2004/index.html ''Lumea Magazin'' Nr 10, 2004]:  (in Romanian; link leads to table of contents, verifying that the article exists, but the article itself is not online).\n*{{in lang|ro}} Viorel Patrichi, \"[https://web.archive.org/web/20041204211613/http://www.lumeam.ro/nr12_2001/politica_si_servicii_secrete.html Eu am fost sosia lui Nicolae Ceau\u0219escu]\" (\"I was Ceau\u0219escu's double\"), ''[[Lumea]]'' Nr 12, 2001\n*{{Cite book | last=Siani-Davies | first=Peter | title=The Romanian Revolution of December 1989 | location=Ithaca, NY | publisher=Cornell University Press | year=2005 (2007) | isbn=0-8014-4245-1 }}\n*{{in lang|ro}} Victor Stanculescu, \"[http://www.jurnalul.ro/articole/59331/victor-stanculescu:-nu-va-fie-mila&-au-doua-miliarde-de-lei-in-cont& Nu v\u0103 fie mil\u0103, au 2 miliarde de lei \u00een cont]\" \"Show no mercy, they have two billion [[Romanian leu|lei]] <nowiki>[</nowiki>33 million U.S. dollars<nowiki>]</nowiki> in their bank account\" in ''[[Jurnalul National|Jurnalul Na\